7. Open the email and click the link to rest the users password.
8. Once the reset-password page is loaded, enter the new password as "ABCD" and confirm the new password as "ABCD".
9. Click the save button.
10. Now enter the new password as "Admin123" and confirm the new password as "Admin456".
11. Click the save button.
12. Now enter the new password as "ad" and confirm the new password as "ad".
13. Click the save button.

** Expected Results **
