2. Confirm that on step 9, when the save button is clicked a message is displayed stating "New password should contain at least 1 character, 1 number, be at least 4 charcters long and not be longer than 8 characters".
3. Confirm that on step 11, when the save button is clicked a message is displayed stating "New password and confirm passwords do not Match"
